%section#wv-community
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-lg-7
        %h1 community
        %p We have many places for you to connect, belong and get involved, no matter what your age or life stage.
        %h2 life groups
        %p Our Life Groups are at the heart of our church. They meet in people's homes in Winchester and the surrounding areas. They are a great place to get to know others, share both the big and the small things of life, and learn to do the things Jesus did.
        %p Groups run on a termly basis, with some groups lasting just a term and other groups lasting longer. You are welcome to continue going to the same group for several terms.

        %h2 how to join a life group
        %p
          We are currently accepting signups for life groups running during the Summer term 2015. Groups start the week of the 4th May, with the Parenting Teenagers group starting a week earlier.

        %p
          %strong Please sign up even if you're planning on going to your existing group!
        %p
          %a.btn.btn-primary{:href => '/lifegroups'} View the list of life groups &raquo;
